name: Agent Simulator
summary: Agents wanted! Would you like to join us? If you are a sharpshooter, you would be a great fit for our team. Within a short period of time, select 3 options from the list and deal with your enemies. Do not forget that the ability of using time efficiently and aiming your targets are crucial. Complete each mission and earn an agent certification at the end. Come on Agent, it is time to prove yourself!
